		<div class="postbody">
			<div class="postrow has_after_content">
				
				
				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					1.0.4 Systems Preview
				</h2>
				

						
							
							
							
						
						
				<div class="content ">
					<div id="post_message_1752488">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							<a href="http://us.battle.net/d3/en/blog/6923456/104_Systems_Preview-8_10_2012" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://us.battle.net/d3/en/blog/6923...view-8_10_2012</a><br />
<br />
Summary:<br />
No more MF averaging in co-op<br />
<br />
75% monster health multiplier in co-op (instead of 110% in Inferno)<br />
<br />
normal monsters +10% health, elites/rares/uniques down 10%-25% health. normal monsters get 4x drop chance buff on items.<br />
<br />
affixes like fire chains and shielding are getting nerfed. invulnerable minions have been removed<br />
<br />
iLvl61 and 62 weapons damage range has been extended to the top of iLvl63<br />
<br />
2h weapons get new stronger affixes to make them not worthless<br />
<br />
no more enrage timers or full heal resets (bosses still have enrage)<br />
<br />
repair costs down by 25%<br />
<br />
no details on changes to legendary items<br />
<br />
skills are getting a complete makeover<br />
<br />
release date fourth week of august
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="after_content">
				
                                       
                                 
				
		        		<blockquote class="signature restore"><div class="signaturecontainer">"Complaining is the modern metagame" - BNet forums</div></blockquote>
				
                                        
			</div>
			
			<div class="cleardiv"></div>
		</div>
	</div>
		<div class="postfoot">
			<!-- <div class="postfoot_container"> -->
